{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"df56a49f78","title":"大字报——院领导对教学是外行","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（一）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"006a2f55fc","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":7,"articleId":"df56a49f78"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f61eadb28f","name":"太原工学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"844ab34947","type":"title","text":"大字报——院领导对教学是外行","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"4c5719f6c4","type":"authors","text":"太原工学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"8e3f3a77ab","type":"paragraph","text":"院领导对教学是外行，不虚心学习业务，对过去表示自大，对别人表示自卑，对自己的教学横加干涉。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"94024428d6","type":"paragraph","text":"听说山西省还有个省委，里面还有个文教部，统率：工、医、师、农“盖世无双”四学院。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"77a2e81865","type":"paragraph","text":"它究竟干些什么名堂？既会吹，又会装，整年睡在沙发上，醒醒吧！先生们。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"d2d69bbfb8","type":"paragraph","text":"高教部目无三小工学院，只顾重点不全面，学术会议没有份，而我院领导唯唯诺诺，唯命是听，根本无争取之心，对此我们表示不满。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"5f2c8d09fc","type":"paragraph","text":"省委鼓励我们“骑毛驴上山”，王中青过于粗暴独行，院长情愿让我们喝白开水亦无进取之心。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"33fe5d84c7","type":"paragraph","text":"我们身在太原——重工业基地之一，有利条件不少，可惜我们是小工学院，命中注定无权利用，不惜花费金钱，流亡他乡！而条件尽为清华所独吞，我们呼吁门户开放。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"70753a49b1","type":"paragraph","text":"科学报告会和学报无内容而且无经费，成为三小工学院独特风格，妙哉！妙哉！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"cb3678785d","type":"paragraph","text":"图书资料奇缺，资料保密的很多，再三呼吁置之不理。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"f15fa84da7","type":"paragraph","text":"有消息称“电机馆，过于庞大”，领导有缩小之意，是这样吗？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"e8c81ce56d","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要求陶鲁笳光临河西。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"},{"id":"920e89dd6b","type":"paragraph","text":" 太原工学院电二一伙人6月7日","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78"}],"page":{"id":"a90c4e64cc","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"df56a49f78","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}